SUMMARY: Coffee & Conversation at Toronto Public Library\, St. Lawrence B
 ranch
DESCRIPTION:Coffee & Conversation at Toronto Public Library\, St. Lawrenc
 e Branch\n\nPlease join library staff for some light refreshments\, and i
 nformal discussion about services in the neighbourhood. Get to know your 
 local library staff and let us know what information and resources you wo
 uld like to access at the library and in the community. A different commu
 nity organization will be onsite each month to share information about th
 eir services. Happening on the second Monday of every month. This July\, 
 we will be hosting 2 SPIRITED PEOPLE OF THE 1ST NATIONS\n\nNo Registratio
 n Required\n\nMonday\, April 13\, 2026\; 1:00-3:00pm\n\nSt. Lawrence Bran
 ch\; 171 Front St E\, Toronto M5A 4H3\; 416-393-765
