SUMMARY: TPL: Finding Recovery Through Exercise Skills and Hope (FRESH)
DESCRIPTION:This Toronto Public Library program helps people stay active\
 , make friends\, learn new skills\, and have fun. Offered in collaboratio
 n with the Gerstein Crisis Centre\, it involves peer-led group activities
  including crafts\, games\, walking\, yoga\, and more.\n\nMeet new folks\
 , build connections\, and tell us about programs and services you would l
 ike to see in the neighbourhood!\n\nOffered on the second Wednesday of ea
 ch month from 1:00 PM until 3:00 PM. Just drop-in. No registration requir
 ed. Refreshments provided.\n\nAsk staff for more information: 416-393-765
 5
